Project Structure
web-vuln-scanner/
├── web_vuln_scanner.py    # Flask app with ZAP integration and routes
├── templates/
│   ├── index.html         # Input form with progress indicator
│   ├── results.html       # Results table and report download link
├── README.md              # Project documentation
├── vuln.db                # SQLite database (generated on first run)
├── report_*.pdf           # Generated PDF reports (excluded in .gitignore)
